.TH TWSU-UPDATE 1 "July 2026" "tw-safe-update 1.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
twsu-update \- run the real Tumbleweed dist-upgrade interactively
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B twsu-update
.SH DESCRIPTION
Runs
.B sudo zypper dist-upgrade
interactively (always asks for your password; review zypper's summary before
confirming), then re-runs
.BR twsu-check (1)
so the tray status reflects the new state. Launched by the tray's
\(lqUpdate now\(rq button inside an embedded terminal, but works in any
terminal.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR twsu-check (1),
.BR twsu-tray (1),
.BR zypper (8)
